Usage: dump_unannotated_nets [-help] [-file <string>] [-type <string>]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-file <string>     # Specifies the output file name where the results will be
                   # dumped (string, optional)
-type <string>     # Specifies the file type to exclude in unannotated report:
                   # activity/cap/vcd/fsdb/tcf/shm/timing/all (string, optional)